description: After 16 seasons, two Olympic gold medals and three WNBA championships, Candace Parker announced her retirement from professional basketball on Sunday.
title: Candace Parker, 3-time WNBA and 2-time Olympic champion, says 'it's time' to retire

description: Police took more than 250 protesters into custody in Arizona, Indiana, Massachusetts and Missouri this weekend, as the war in Gaza continues to embroil campuses across the nation.
title: Nearly 300 people arrested at campus protests against the war in Gaza this weekend
